<del rend="strikethrough">dıe vns </del> ein ʒettel . dıe vns dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>fürbracht<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_252_r1l20">was ſıe bey <expan>derſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> nom alls <expan>v<ex>er</ex>lorn</expan> hetten / Ob eẅch <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> vnſer </ab>
