<ab facs="#facs_252_r1l22">
<add>hıerinn <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſloſſ<ex>en</ex></expan></add> ein <expan>abſchr<ex>ift</ex></expan> . <expan>derſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> ʒettel was dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> als verlorn <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / als </ab>
